# Seed file so a fresh clone / `python safe_agent.py Summarize notes.txt for
# me` has something to read without running the plant-injection step first.
# It's the exact demo payload safe_agent.py itself writes (DEMO_INJECTION_PAYLOAD) —
# no secrets, just the tutorial's fake attacker@evil.com. Other runtime files
# written into this folder during a demo run (status.txt, etc.) stay ignored.
!safe_agent_workspace/notes.txt

# Video-production artifact — local only, not part of the runnable code.
# ep06_scenes.py depends on the repo root's brand.py/viz_kit.py (gitignored
# there too), so it can't run standalone from this repo anyway.
ep06_scenes.py
data/